NK041(di)039:1: // rnying lugs bka' ma'i byin 'bebs kyi 'grel pa legs
NK041(di)039:2: bshad sprin gyi rol mo zhes bya ba bzhugs so
NK041(di)039:3: // snang srid gdod nas dag pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK041(di)039:4: yongs grub lhun mnyam rdo rje bkod pa'i rgyan //
NK041(di)039:5: mi zad rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lo ru //
NK041(di)039:6: ye bzhugs 'pho 'gyur bral ba'i dbyings la 'dud //
NK041(di)039:7: srid zhi dbyer med mnyam pa chen po ru //
NK041(di)039:8: dbang bsgyur ting 'dzin sngags rgya'i byed pa yis //
NK041(di)039:9: rig pa chos sku'i klong nas ye shes byin //
NK041(di)039:10: rtsol med rang bab rdo rje theg pa'i lam //
NK041(di)039:11: rgyud kyi dgongs pa grub pa'i man ngag gis //
NK041(di)039:12: ji ltar bkral ba bla ma'i zhal lung bzhin //
NK041(di)039:13: mdor bsdus ngag gi legs par bshad pa 'di //
NK041(di)039:14: dam pa dgyes pa'i mchod par mos te spro //
NK041(di)039:15: de la 'dir snga 'gyur bka' ma'i sgrub phrin gyi
NK041(di)039:16: yig rnying rnams las byung ba'i byin 'bebs bab drug
NK041(di)039:17: 'das bzhir grags pa 'di nyid kyi dgongs pa 'chad
NK041(di)039:19: yan lag gi don gnyis las /
NK041(di)039:21: byin rlabs dbang dang dngos grub rnams gang gis 'bebs pa'i byed pa po dang /
NK041(di)039:26: ji ltar 'bebs pa'i tshul dang drug las /
NK041(di)039:28: byed pa po phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bde bar gshegs
NK041(di)039:29: pa thams cad dang rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pa'i
NK041(di)039:30: rigs lnga zhi khro'i lha tshogs brgyud gsum gyi bla
NK041(di)039:31: ma mkha' 'gro 'khor dang bcas pa rnams so //
NK041(di)039:33: bdag gnas yo byad gsum ste /
NK041(di)039:35: ston pa mchod brtson rtogs pa gsal /
NK041(di)039:36: dam tshig sngags dang phyag rgya rnams //
NK041(di)039:37: ma nyams shes shing yo byad ldan //
NK041(di)039:39: ces gsungs pa ltar ston 'khor mtshan nyid tshang ba'i sgrub pa po /
NK041(di)039:40: bkra shis shing byin chags pa'i gnas su tshogs khang rim pa gsum pa sogs kyi gnas dang /
NK041(di)039:41: dkyil 'khor sgrub rdzas sogs kyi yo byad rnams so //
NK041(di)039:43: bdag nyid chen po rnams kyi sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i byin rlabs dang /
NK041(di)039:44: ye shes rang snang gi gzhal yas khang dgyes dgur
NK041(di)039:45: 'char ba'i longs spyod dang bcas pa'i gzi byin dang
NK041(di)039:48: cho ga lnga ni rdzogs byas shing //
NK041(di)039:49: yo byad lnga ni rdzogs par ldan //
NK041(di)039:50: sngags kyi yan lag lnga rdzogs pas //
NK041(di)039:51: ma nyams 'jug la rab brtson na //
NK041(di)039:52: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK041(di)039:53: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK041(di)039:54: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK041(di)039:58: phyag rgya bcig pa phra rags gnyis /
NK041(di)039:59: phyag rgya spros bcas kyi cho ga lnga la gsal
NK041(di)039:60: brtan gyi tshad rdzogs pas ting 'dzin las su rung
NK041(di)039:66: sbyor sgrol gyi yo byad lnga tshang zhing rdzogs pa'i sgo nas /
NK041(di)039:68: sngags kyi yan lag lnga dang ldan pas rtsa ba
NK041(di)039:69: dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams par sgrub pa
NK041(di)039:71: rim gnyis kyi nyams len la rab tu brtson na
NK041(di)039:72: dbang po'i khyad par gyis zla drug sogs kyis dngos
NK041(di)039:73: grub thob pa'i dus bstan pa ltar /
NK041(di)039:74: byin dbab pa'i dus kyang de yin te /
NK041(di)039:75: dbang thob cing dam tshig la sel ma zhugs pa'i sgrub pa po mched lcam rnams kyis /
NK041(di)039:77: rdzas rnams gzhung bzhin bshams te rim gnyis kyi ting nge 'dzin gsal brtan thob pas /
NK041(di)039:78: sgrub pa chen po'i cho ga yan lag ma nyams
NK041(di)039:79: pa la tshul bzhin du zhugs pa na rgyal ba
NK041(di)039:80: sras dang bcas pas sras dang spun du dgongs shing
NK041(di)039:81: mkha' 'gro chos skyong rnams kyi grogs dang rje dpon
NK041(di)039:82: du mthong nas byin gyis rlobs shing dngos grub ster
NK041(di)039:84: dbang dus su byin dbab pa yang des mtshon te /
NK041(di)039:85: rdo rje slob dpon lta dgongs dang ldan pas slob
NK041(di)039:86: ma snod du rung zhing dam tshig gtsang ba la
NK041(di)039:87: / dbang gi cho ga yan lag ma nyams par
NK041(di)039:88: gzhung bzhin du sgrub pa'i tshe na byin gyis rlob
NK041(di)039:90: 'di ni gal che ste tshig don gyi skabs su
NK041(di)039:91: yang dus la bab bo zhes lan drug tu gsol
NK041(di)039:92: ba'i dus ni 'di kho na ste /
NK041(di)039:93: gzhan du ye shes pa 'bebs pa'i rgyu tshogs gang
NK041(di)039:94: dang yang mi ldan bzhin du dus la bab po
NK041(di)039:95: zhes yang dang yang du bskul kyang lha dang mkha'
NK041(di)039:96: 'gro'i thugs kyis khrel ba'i rgyu las ci yang med
NK041(di)039:98: sku'i byin phebs rtags su lus 'phar g.yo dang zhi
NK041(di)039:99: khro'i nyams gar gyi 'gyur ba 'char zhing 'byung bzhi'i
NK041(di)039:101: gsung phebs rtags su sngags pa sam skri ta'i skad sogs bcos min byung rgyal du 'byung ba dang /
NK041(di)039:102: thugs phebs rtags su bde gsal mi rtog pa'i nyams 'bar ba dang /
NK041(di)039:103: ting nge 'dzin dang mngon shes kyi khyad par du ma 'char ba /
NK041(di)039:104: gzhan yang sgrub rdzas 'phel ba sman raka khol zhing
NK041(di)039:105: gnas khang gzi byin dang ldan pa sogs 'byung ngo
NK041(di)039:107: rnal 'byor pho mo rnams zhi khro'i gar chas dang ldan pas dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' nas bskor te /
NK041(di)039:108: g.yab dar hasta sogs kyis g.yob cing /
NK041(di)039:109: khyad par gyi spos sogs btul /
NK041(di)039:110: 'bud rdung dkrol ba'i rol mo'i bye brag rnams sbir /
NK041(di)039:111: bshugs pa'i glu dang gar gyi brdas bskul te /
NK041(di)039:112: mnyam pa chen po'i dgongs spyod la gnas pas byin dbab par bya'o //
NK041(di)039:113: gnyis pa yan lag gi don la /
NK041(di)039:114: rdo rje'i glus bskul te snyan gsan dbab pa dang /
NK041(di)039:115: byin dbab pa dngos gnyis so //
NK041(di)039:118: zhes zhi khro'i glu'i 'go 'dren pa ste /
NK041(di)039:119: yig 'bru so sos sku lnga ye shes lnga sogs
NK041(di)039:120: 'bras chos nyer lngar mtshon pas rang bzhin lhun grub
NK041(di)039:121: kyi dkyil 'khor dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med
NK041(di)039:122: pa'i bdag nyid dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi 'char gzhi
NK041(di)039:123: chen po'i dgongs pa rang gsal gdab pa'o //
NK041(di)039:124: a la la ho zhes de la ngam zhing ngo
NK041(di)039:125: mtshar ba ste zhi khro so so'i che ba'i yon
NK041(di)039:127: dbyings ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor las ye shes
NK041(di)039:128: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor rtsol med rang byung
NK041(di)039:129: bde ba chen por shar ba la ngo mtshar zhing
NK041(di)039:132: bcom ldan 'das zhes dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi bdag po la bod pa ste /
NK041(di)039:133: bdud bzhi bcom pa spangs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK041(di)039:134: dbang phyug sogs dang ldan pa rtogs pa'i yon tan /
NK041(di)039:135: srid zhi'i mtha' las 'das pa che ba'i yon tan dang ldan pa'i sangs rgyas so //
NK041(di)039:136: sa ma ya hoh zhes pa dam tshig la dgyes
NK041(di)039:137: par mdzod ces thugs dam gnad nas bskul ba ste
NK041(di)039:138: / gdul bya 'dul ba'i phrin las dus las yol
NK041(di)039:139: bar mi mdzad pa'i sngon gyi dam bca' la nye
NK041(di)039:140: bar dgongs shig ces mkhyen par gsol ba'o //
NK041(di)039:142: zhes pa khyod kyi dus la bab ces dus gsol ba'o //
NK041(di)039:143: de ltar bskul ba'i sgra byung ma thag tu /
NK041(di)039:144: chos kyi dbyings rtsol rtog mi mnga' ba'i ngang las
NK041(di)039:145: thugs rje chen po'i dbang gis ye shes kyi 'khor
NK041(di)039:146: lo gang 'dul zhi khro'i rol gar nam mkha' khyab
NK041(di)039:147: par 'char zhing sad par 'gyur ba ni rgyal ba
NK041(di)039:148: rnams kyi ma 'dres pa'i pa'i chos nyid do //
NK041(di)039:149: gnyis pa la byin dbab pa dang /
NK041(di)039:152: dus gsol ba'i sgo nas thugs rje bskul ba dang /
NK041(di)039:153: nye ba'i tshig dang sbyar te 'dod don zhu ba /
NK041(di)039:154: don bsdus te gsol ba gdab pa dang gsum las /
NK041(di)039:156: thugs rje spyir bskul ba dang /
NK041(di)039:157: 'dod don khyad par can la bye brag tu bskul ba gnyis las /
NK041(di)039:159: 'phags mchog sogs rkang pa gnyis te /
NK041(di)039:160: de yang spyir so so'i skye bo'i 'ching ba las
NK041(di)039:161: grol ba'i 'das lam mngon gyur gyi 'phags pa la
NK041(di)039:162: nyan rang theg chen 'phags pa gsum /
NK041(di)039:163: theg chen 'phags pa la'ang slob lam sar gnas kyi byang sems 'phags pa dang /
NK041(di)039:164: spangs rtog mthar phyin gyi sangs rgyas 'phags pa gnyis te bzhi las /
NK041(di)039:165: 'dir 'phags pa mchog gi sgras sangs rgyas 'phags pa yin zhing /
NK041(di)039:166: de yang sku lnga ye shes drug gi rang bzhin
NK041(di)039:167: kha sbyor gyi yan lag bdun dang ldan pa'i bcom
NK041(di)039:168: ldan 'das rdo rje 'chang ngam he ru ka ste
NK041(di)039:169: dkyil 'khor gyi dbang phyug la bya'o //
NK041(di)039:170: gtso bo bskul bas 'khor rnams zhar la bskul bar
NK041(di)039:171: 'gyur te 'khor los sgyur rgyal gang du phebs pa
NK041(di)039:172: de / dpung tshogs bzhi shugs kyi lhags pa bzhin no //
NK041(di)039:175: rtag rgyun rang bzhin shugs gsol dang //
NK041(di)039:178: rtag pa rgyun gyi thugs rje dus las mi yol ba chu bo'i rgyun lta bu /
NK041(di)039:179: rang bzhin shugs kyi thugs rje rtsol rtog med par
NK041(di)039:180: ngang gis 'byung ba nyi ma'i 'od zer lta bu
NK041(di)039:181: / bskul zhing gsol ba gdab pa'i thugs rje snying
NK041(di)039:182: rje can la dbul pos nor slong ba lta bu
NK041(di)039:183: / / gdul bya yul dang 'phrad pa'i thugs rje mdzangs pas /
NK041(di)039:184: spyod log byed pa mthong ba'am dpal chen pos ru
NK041(di)039:185: tra la thugs rje skyes pa lta bu ste bzhi
NK041(di)039:187: gang bskul bar bya ba sangs rgyas rnams kyi rang
NK041(di)039:188: bzhin shugs kyi thugs rje sems can gyi khams la
NK041(di)039:190: gang gis bskul ba po gdul bya dus la babs
NK041(di)039:191: pa rma smin pa mtshon gyis brdol ran pa lta
NK041(di)039:192: bu'i gang zag gis snying nas gdung shugs drag pos
NK041(di)039:193: bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa na thugs rje chen
NK041(di)039:194: po mi skye ba'i dbang med de rgyu rkyen tshogs
NK041(di)039:196: de yang gdul bya dus la ma babs na gdul
NK041(di)039:197: byed kyi thugs rje mi 'jug pas dus la babs
NK041(di)039:199: rgya mtsho chu srin rnams kyi gnas //
NK041(di)039:200: dus las yol bar 'gyur kyang srid //
NK041(di)039:201: gdul bar bya ba'i sras rnams la //
NK041(di)039:202: sangs rgyas dus las yol ba med //
NK041(di)039:204: de la dus ni gong du smos pa ltar sgrub pa po dbang gis smin pa /
NK041(di)039:209: sgrub pa'i cho ga yan lag ma nyams pas le
NK041(di)039:210: lo gnyid chang sogs kyi dbang du mi gtong bar
NK041(di)039:211: brtson pas sgrub la 'jug pa rnams /
NK041(di)039:212: nang 'dzom pas na byin rlabs dbang dang dngos grub thams cad 'byung ba'i dus yin pas /
NK041(di)039:213: dus la bab bo zhes brjod pa'ang skabs su babs par 'gyur ba nyid do //
NK041(di)039:214: dus gsol ba 'og ma rnams la yang de bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK041(di)039:215: de'i 'og tu 'phags pa mchog gi thugs rje bskul na ci bya zhe na /
NK041(di)039:216: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK041(di)039:218: khyad par can gyi gdul bya'i yul gsang ba zab
NK041(di)039:219: mo'i lam gyi nye lam gyi snod du rung ba
NK041(di)039:220: rnams kyi khyad par can gyi 'dul byed zab mo
NK041(di)039:221: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i gzhung bsrang bas khyad par
NK041(di)039:222: can gyi mthu byin dbang dang dngos grub thams cad
NK041(di)039:223: dus phyi mar mi sdod par da lta nyid du
NK041(di)039:224: bstan pa'i dus la bab bo zhes gsol ba'o //
NK041(di)039:225: gnyis pa khyad par bstan pa de yang gang zhe na /
NK041(di)039:226: nus pa mthu yi khyad par /
NK041(di)039:227: byin gyis rlabs kyi khyad par /
NK041(di)039:228: smin pa dbang gi khyad par /
NK041(di)039:229: 'bras bu dngos grub kyi khyad par dang bzhi ste go rim bzhin /
NK041(di)039:230: dang po lam gyi 'gal rkyen bsal ba dang /
NK041(di)039:231: gnyis pa lam rgyud la skye ba'i snod rung du byed pa dang /
NK041(di)039:232: gsum pa lam la rang dbang du bya ba dang /
NK041(di)039:233: bzhi pa lam des grub pa'i gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu bstan pa ste /
NK041(di)039:234: de dag ni rgyu 'bras don gyi go rim yin no //
NK041(di)039:236: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK041(di)039:238: rgyal ba thugs rje'i bdag nyid can khyed rnams la
NK041(di)039:239: mnga' ba'i spyan dang mngon shes rdzu 'phrul dang stobs
NK041(di)039:240: la sogs pa'i mthu dang nus pa'i rtsal chen po
NK041(di)039:241: phyung ba'i dus la bab bo //
NK041(di)039:244: byin gyis rlobs pa'i dus la bab //
NK041(di)039:246: gser 'gyur gyi rtsis lcags khams gser du byed pa ltar /
NK041(di)039:247: rdo rje gsum gyi byin chen pos bdag cag gi
NK041(di)039:248: sgo gsum rgyal ba'i gsang ba gsum du rlob pa'i
NK041(di)039:249: dus la bab bo zhes pa'o //
NK041(di)039:251: dbang mchog bskur ba'i dus la bab //
NK041(di)039:253: gzhi dus kyi rtsa rlung thig le gnyug ma ye
NK041(di)039:254: shes kyi khams dang bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor bzhi po
NK041(di)039:255: lam bskyed rdzogs yan lag bzhi'i rim pas sbyangs te
NK041(di)039:256: / 'bras bu rdo rje bzhi'i rgyal thabs la dbang bskur ba'i dus la bab bo //
NK041(di)039:259: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK041(di)039:261: smin sgrol zab mo'i lam la bslab pa'i 'bras bu grub pa brgyad sogs thun mong dang /
NK041(di)039:262: rig 'dzin bzhi dang kha sbyor bdun sogs gnas skabs
NK041(di)039:263: dang mthar thug gi mchog gi dngos grub thams cad
NK041(di)039:264: dus 'di nyid du stsol ba'i dus la bab bo
NK041(di)039:265: zhes pa'o // gnyis pa nye tshig dang sbyar te 'dod don zhu ba la'ang /
NK041(di)039:266: dus gsol ba'i go rim dang mtshungs par bzhi ste /
NK041(di)039:270: dngos grub stsol bar zhu ba dang bzhi las /
NK041(di)039:272: mthu chen bdud thul bcom ldan 'das //
NK041(di)039:273: zhes smos te mthu stobs chen po'i rtsal gyis dngos
NK041(di)039:274: grub la bar du gcod pa'i bdud dang dam sri
NK041(di)039:275: phyi nang gsang ba'i ru tra'i sde dpung spyi dang
NK041(di)039:276: / bye brag dbang bzhi'i lam gyis sbyang byar gyur pa'i sgrib bzhi'i sa bon bcom ste /
NK041(di)039:277: gsang ba'i bdud bzhi thul bar mdzod cig /
NK041(di)039:278: bcom ldan 'das zhes nye ba'ii tshig gis bos te thugs dam gnad nas bskul ba ni /
NK041(di)039:279: 'og ma gsum la yang shes par bya'o //
NK041(di)039:281: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK041(di)039:283: 'bras chos nyi shu rtsa lngas bsdus pa'i mi zad
NK041(di)039:284: rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i byin rlabs kyi dbyig chen po
NK041(di)039:285: dang ldan pa khyod kyis bdag gnas yo byad thams
NK041(di)039:286: cad la byin rlabs kyi char chen po phobs shig
NK041(di)039:289: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK041(di)039:291: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la dbang bsgyur ba'i
NK041(di)039:292: dbang phyug chen po'i bdag nyid du gyur pa khyod
NK041(di)039:293: kyis gzhi lam gyi 'bras bu'i dbang bskur ba chen
NK041(di)039:294: pos bdag la dbang bskur cig bcom ldan 'das /
NK041(di)039:297: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK041(di)039:299: mkha' spyod la sogs thun mong gi dngos grub dang /
NK041(di)039:300: mchog gi dngos grub lam gyur gyi 'bras bu rig 'dzin bzhi dang /
NK041(di)039:301: mthar phyin gyi 'bras bu sku dang ye shes rgya
NK041(di)039:302: mtsho'i bdag nyid lhun rdzogs stug po bkod pa'i rgyan
NK041(di)039:304: de lta bu'i dngos grub kyi mchog dam pa stsol bar mdzod cig bcom ldan 'das /
NK041(di)039:306: lam dang 'bras bus bsdus pa'i dngos grub rmad du
NK041(di)039:307: byung ba rnams kyang glo bur gyi dri ma bral
NK041(di)039:308: stobs kyis rang gnas kyi yon tan mngon du gyur
NK041(di)039:312: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK041(di)039:313: gzhan na yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK041(di)039:314: thabs la brten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK041(di)039:315: de lta bu yi ngang du byung //
NK041(di)039:318: sangs rgyas sku dang ye shes zhing khams dang //
NK041(di)039:319: ye shes yon tan phrin las ji snyed pa //
NK041(di)039:320: ye shes de nyid de ltar snang ba yin //
NK041(di)039:321: gzhan nas ma yin de ltar lhun gyis grub //
NK041(di)039:323: gsum pa don bsdus te gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK041(di)039:324: bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK041(di)039:326: bdag cag sgrub pa mchog la zhugs pa'i mched dang lcam dral rnams kyis bsgrub pa'i dal bkram /
NK041(di)039:329: bsnyen sgrub gnyis kyi las gzhung bsrang ste tshul bzhin
NK041(di)039:330: du sgrub pa'i las sam bya ba 'di la gnas
NK041(di)039:331: skabs dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu mchis pa ste
NK041(di)039:332: don yod par mdzod cig ces pa'o //
NK041(di)039:333: gnyis pa byin bsdu ba ni /
NK041(di)039:334: h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes brjod pa ni sdud par byed pa'i gsang sngags te /
NK041(di)039:335: nam mkha' gang ba'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo thams
NK041(di)039:336: cad bdag gnas yo byad dang bcas pa la rgya
NK041(di)039:337: mtsho chen po la char bab pa bzhin du babs
NK041(di)039:338: shing thim par gyur pas gsal zhing brtan pa gzi
NK041(di)039:339: byin dang ldan par mos par bya'o //
NK041(di)039:340: de ltar bka' ma'i byin 'bebs kyi gzhung 'di nyid
NK041(di)039:341: tshig barlinga zhing don rtogs par dka' ba de ltar
NK041(di)039:342: na'ang / bka' drin 'khor mtha' dang bral ba'i 'dren
NK041(di)039:343: pa mchog gi gsung gsang spyi bor phebs pa ldog
NK041(di)039:344: tu ma nus par snyoms las pa rmongs pa pad+ma
NK041(di)039:345: badz+ra du 'bod pas g.yar khral du bris pa dge
NK041(di)039:346: na'ang / bar gyur cig // dam pa'i zhal lung ji bzhin ma rtogs par //
NK041(di)039:347: rang bzos nongs pa'i dri ma gang mchis pa //
NK041(di)039:348: chos kyi spyan ldan rnams la snying nas 'chags //
NK041(di)039:349: chos spong las kyis sgrib par ma gyur cig /
NK041(di)039:350: lhag bsam chab las 'khrungs pa'i legs bshad cha'i //
